    rv "And my side job is that of a cat detective."


translate English rv2_b38ba66e:


    pl "What the heck is a cat detective???"


translate English rv2_d665f416:


    rv "Why, it's a job where I find lost runaway kittens and return them to their families! Simple as that!"


translate English rv2_d7b264af:


    pl "So that's it, huh? You're just good at everything."


translate English rv2_a4cc4322:


    pl "Isn't it hard for someone afflicted by the pestis to live a normal life?"


translate English rv2_434f9b17:


    rv "I suppose I'd be lying if I said it wasn't a hindrance at times. It does present several obstacles to my work, after all."


translate English rv2_734289cb:


    pl "How long have you been like this?"


translate English rv2_b08af0a8:


    rv "Since I was very young. Not since I was born, but... "


translate English rv2_8a0ca2ff:


    rv "I've been this way since about the time my parents were caught in the pestis and passed away."


