    rv "Such accidents are commonplace outside the capital."


translate English rv2_714b345a:


    pl "Oh... I thought you were born here. "


translate English rv2_47bf94fd:


    pl "I guess because of your... I don't know, your image? I'm surprised to hear you had a rough upbringing."


translate English rv2_7abe9ac8:


    rv "I'm honored that you view it positively. But I certainly haven't led that difficult a life."


translate English rv2_aef7e4e2:


    rv "Before, the only things I could do well were fiddle with machines and study. But even with just that special skill, I get by pretty well."


translate English rv2_0a4de4a9:


    rv "I'm also quite good at brewing tea. Ah, and I know how to juggle to some extent."


translate English rv2_e6c9ad84:


    pl "Modesty or arrogance--I wish you'd pick one or the other!"


translate English rv2_d0f0646c:


    rv "Heh heh heh."


translate English rv2_7868dbef:


    pl "Seriously, it kind of stinks that someone as talented as you has the pestis."


translate English rv2_28e806d7:


    rv "Perhaps so, but God has decided that this is to be my fate. "


translate English rv2_37022611:


    rv "Even in the slim chance that it prevents me from accomplishing something..."


translate English rv2_79ab7f4f:


    rv "I believe it will be due to my own lack of ability, not the pestis."


