    gg "As far as the Health Department goes... As I'm sure you're aware, the folks here assist the priests who work here in the temple."


translate English gg1_1a943507:


    gg "We primarily help with treating patients in the temple hospital while also assisting with minor inconveniences incurred by our priests throughout the day."


translate English gg1_b23172d1:


    pl "What exactly constitutes a minor inconvenience?"


translate English gg1_9c2265a8:


    gg "Adding addition pockets to clothes, reattaching lost buttons..."


translate English gg1_cfd63677:


    gg "We even do the laundry for all those towels, sheets, and blankets that you leave carelessly strewn about!"


translate English gg1_216500c4:


    pl "So the Health Department is also laundromat, too?"


translate English gg1_840ed885:


    gg "Ding ding ding! We're also in charge of mending your well-worn clothing along with your mental problems. {w}Oh, and we're also in charge of coming up with the menus for each meal of the day."


translate English gg1_63dc6f56:


    pl "Really? In that case, I want more apple pie, pronto!"


translate English gg1_3224f45a:


    gg "It's guys like you that make me feel like this job is a waste of time."


translate English gg1_8a950c4f:


    pl "That's how I've felt this whole time..."


translate English gg1_b9d15d4c:


    pl "Regardless, the delicate nature of the job doesn't seem to suit an old geezer like you who constantly reeks of cigarettes."


translate English gg1_4e5d17b0:


    pl "How did you even get the position of bishop anyway?"


