    gg "It's hard to believe that was eight years ago. {w}I had planned on quitting my position as a priest here and was about to return to my hometown."


translate English gg1_826b40fd:


    gg "The timing of which perfectly coincided with the former bishop's retirement. Imagine that! {w}Upon hearing the news, the Cardinal went and promoted me to fill his spot."


translate English gg1_cc608178:


    gg "And by stepping into the new role, it simultaneously solved a rather big problem of mine as well."


translate English gg1_5745f080:


    pl "You must have been a fairly competent priest to get promoted to bishop."


